MDcache
-------
  Enable/Disable/Flush write cache of MD DATA device.
SYNTAX:
  mdcache [-?] [drive:] ON | OFF | IS | FLUSH
PARAMETERS:
  drive:
    specifies MD DATA device
  ON
    enables write cache
  OFF
    disables write cache
  IS
    reports current state of write cache
  FLUSH
    writes cache to MD DATA disc
SWITCHES:
  -?  this message
EXAMPLES:
  mdcache d: is
  mdcache d: on
  mdcache d: off
CAVEATS:
VERSION:
  1.0
MDcache END
