MDformat
--------
  Format an MD DATA disc
SYNTAX:
  mdformat drive: [-q|s] [-v:label -o -?]
PARAMETERS:
  drive:  specifies drive containing the disc that you wish to format
SWITCHES:
  -q  installs file system, does not certify the media, 1 minute, default
  -s  certifies the media and installs file system, 35 minutes
  -o  obedient, asks no questions
  -v:label  installs volume label after format, 31 characters
  -?  help
EXAMPLES:
  mdformat d: -q
  mdformat d: -s
  mdformat d: -qo
  mdformat d: -qv:YourLabel
CAVEATS:
VERSION:
  1.95
MDformat END
